nodes.text: Net'lseb Toli Park was a park located on the Gar'glum Sea, on the outskirts of Gal'fian'deprisi City on Galantos. It was a kilometer-wide garden of toli trees, fragrant blossoms, and wildlife enclosed in an energy perimeter. The park was a primary tourist attraction among Fia from other parts of the planet, as it had a security force that shot any skree-skaters that approached.
